{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 23,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Always I had sexual-- I was very good in that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which experience?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Women-- this you have it, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The smell-- the smell of the bodies, or something like that?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not too much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, there is some connections with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can-- I can smell very good when there's something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't think there is too much to do with it, what happened in the camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nightmares?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And especially a few years in the beginning, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I used to come, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you read Maria Modiano's letter, you'll see that I-- I used to come out at night and scream and things like that from the nightmares.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nightmares always from the camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, nobody leaves you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whatever is inside of me from that period never leaves you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Always, always I have you in, attached.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I went wild in the world, you know, whatever I could do to always-- I'd never stay home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Always I was traveling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was always busy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mind was busy, not because-- whenever I used to go, you know, for many, many years I used to go to the colleges all around here, to the universities.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever I finished that, for one week I was-- always something at night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It affects me-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm always shaking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even now.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why-- why the-- the Germans that I-- they don't give me enough to be able to go-- you know, $500 a month.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it's nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's whatever I saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever I did doesn't-- I don't want to reapply that to me, because I had nothing to do with it, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
